{
  "id": "adv_event_2406_01_01",
  "title": "決戦前夜",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月のテンペストとどりきゅんの決戦前夜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――It’s the night before the Moon Tempest vs. DoriKyun live battle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 3.3999999523,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2800
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん、何してるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan‚ what are you doing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.6,
      "endTime": 6.2506577015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "月を眺めていたのよ\n今夜はよく見えるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was looking at the moon.\nI can see it clearly tonight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.4373243014,
      "endTime": 11.068548743000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "本当だ……月……綺麗だね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow… The moon… It's beautiful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.2752153237,
      "endTime": 17.2856459458,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、さくらと二人きりで話すのは久し振りね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that you mention it‚ this is the first time we've talked alone in a while‚ Sakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.4723125457,
      "endTime": 21.771587038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね。琴乃ちゃんが月ストに復帰してから\nゆっくり話すのはこれが初めてかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're right. This might be the first time we've talked properly\nsince you rejoined Moon Tempest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.9782535712,
      "endTime": 30.134285465999998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "……いよいよ明日だね\nどりきゅんとのライブバトル",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It's finally tomorrow.\nThe live battle with DoriKyun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.3209523042,
      "endTime": 36.1333786805,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "ええ……\n今だから言うけど、さくらには感謝してるのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah…\nI couldn't say this until now‚ but thank you‚ Sakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.3467119853,
      "endTime": 42.4327665965,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "私が月ストを脱退した時\nさくらは出て行く私を引き留めなかったでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I left Moon Tempest‚\nyou didn't stop me when I was leaving.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.6327665965,
      "endTime": 48.9575058619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "月ストのみんなを説得するのは大変だったから\nさくらが何も言わずに受け入れてくれてありがたかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It must have been hard to convince everyone in Moon Tempest‚\nso I was grateful that you accepted it without saying anything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.1708393096,
      "endTime": 57.096530723499995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "えーと……誤解してるみたいだけど、私も琴乃ちゃんが\n月ストを辞めるのには猛反対してたんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… It seems like you're misunderstanding‚\nbut I was also strongly against you leaving Moon Tempest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.2898639996,
      "endTime": 67.3746712048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "え？\nでも、そんなこと私は聞いてないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?\nBut I didn't hear anything like that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.5813380241,
      "endTime": 72.30863943099999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、琴乃ちゃんには話してなかったね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that you mention it‚ I didn't tell you‚ Kotono-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.5019727071,
      "endTime": 77.10537417729999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんが月ストを辞めるって聞いた時\n私がどう思って、何をしたのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "About what I thought and what I did‚ when I heard‚\nyou were leaving Moon Tempest…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.3187074821,
      "endTime": 84.5809295814,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――琴乃の月のテンペスト脱退が決まった直後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Right after it was decided that Kotono would leave Moon Tempest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.580929486,
      "endTime": 87.5542631309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんが月ストを抜けるって本当なの！？\nどうしてそんなことになったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is it true that Kotono's leaving Moon Tempest!?\nHow did that happen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.4475979329,
      "endTime": 94.3392531872,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "月ストを出て個人で活動したいと\n琴乃ちゃんが言い出したんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan said she wanted to leave\nMoon Tempest and go solo.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.5325865587,
      "endTime": 100.08043220840001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "同じことを続けていても月ストは強くなれない\n今必要なのは強い「個」の力だから、って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She said that Moon Tempest wouldn't get any stronger if they kept doing the same thing.\nand said what we needed now was the strong “individuals”…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.2870989323,
      "endTime": 108.6839474202,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "だからって月ストを辞めるなんて間違ってるよ！\n……私、琴乃ちゃんと話してくる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But that doesn't mean it's right for her to leave Moon Tempest!\n…I'm going to talk to Kotono-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.8706139725,
      "endTime": 118.854355542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "お待ちなさい\n琴乃と話してどうする気ですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold on a second.\nWhat are you going to say Kotono?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.0410223803,
      "endTime": 123.3756707987,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "月ストを辞めないでってお願いするんだよ\n琴乃ちゃんがいなくなるなんて絶対ダメなんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm going to ask her not to leave Moon Tempest.\nWe can’t just let Kotono-chan leave.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.5690040749,
      "endTime": 131.394060914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃんが私達のことを思って\n言ってくれてるのは分かるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand that you’re saying this\nbecause you care about us‚ Sakura-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.5807274661,
      "endTime": 136.3958975634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、これはみんなで話し合って納得したことなの\nお願いだから、琴乃ちゃんの思うようにさせてあげて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But we all talked about this together and agreed on it.\nPlease‚ let Kotono-chan do as she thinks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.6025642874,
      "endTime": 146.7916576864,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "どうして……？\nみんなは琴乃ちゃんと離れ離れになってもいいの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why…?\nAre you all okay with being separated from Kotono-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.9783244294,
      "endTime": 153.8140614671,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "私達だって離れたくありませんわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course we don’t want to be separated!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.0140616578,
      "endTime": 157.6948325795,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんがいなくなってもいいなんて\n誰も思ってないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No one’s saying it’s okay\nfor Kotono-chan to be gone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.8948326749,
      "endTime": 162.5754221601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "私達だって辛いんです\nでも、琴乃ちゃんだって私達と同じくらい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're hurting too.\nBut Kotono-chan is just as hurt as we are…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.7687553885,
      "endTime": 170.05220198659998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "いいえ、決断した琴乃ちゃん自身が\n誰よりも悩んで苦しんだはずなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ Kotono-chan‚ the one who made the decision‚\nmust have been troubled and suffered even more than any of us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.2455351673,
      "endTime": 176.7391634784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "五人で進めたら一番いいってことは\n私達も……琴乃ちゃんも分かってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We know… and Kotono-chan knows…\nthat it’s best to move forward with five members.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.9524969263,
      "endTime": 184.1095492524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
